title: Pirates of the Caribbean Dead Men Tell No Tales 2017 HD-TS x265
description:
Using the "Pirates of the Caribbean Dead Men Tell No Tales 2017 PROPER HD-TS x264-CPG" 2.2gb file as a base, I ran it through Vidcoder with an x265 preset, slight upsizing (to 1024 width) and a wee bit of de-noising and de-blocking.

Result: still blurry as fuck, but now way smaller! -- Because if there's one thing you greedy little piglets appreciate, it's getting your swag in only 40% of the time
